
2026-03-21: For cold outreach and casual prose, add natural imperfections: "40 something" instead of "approximately 40", contractions like "its" vs "it's", lowercase "im". Avoid vendor-dumping (listing every tool name). Use spoken idioms ("hit home", "swap notes", "funny enough"). Stream-of-consciousness with purpose reads more human than rigid structure. Domain-specific density without lecturing = excited peer, not a model summarizing a blog post.
